      Description

      The San Francisco 49ers are a professional American football team based in the San Francisco Bay Area. The 49ers compete in the National Football League as a member of the league's National Football Conference West division. Wikipedia
      NFL championships: 1995, 1990, 1989, 1985, 1982
      Head coach: Kyle Shanahan
      Arena/Stadium: Levi's Stadium
      Owner: Denise DeBartolo York
      CEO: Jed York
      Chairman: Denise DeBartolo York; John York (co-chairs)
